author: Jordyn Tilchen
title: Joe Jonas And Sophie Turner Reveal Who Fell In Love First In TikTok ‘Couples Challenge’
description: Yesterday (April 15), Joe Jonas and Sophie Turner took part in a 'couples challenge' on TikTok. The pair revealed who's the grumpiest and who fell in love first in the short and adorable clip.
content: It's only been a couple of days since TikTok's royal couple, Charli D'Amelio and Chase Hudson (a.k.a. Lil Huddy), called it quits on their relationship. But things happen fast on the internet, and it looks like there's a new couple ready to take the throne: J… [+1512 chars]
